cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper deals with generating and predicting sequences of images, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) and Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) also suggests that it may fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the use of diagrams and abstract reasoning may suggest a connection to graph theory (cs.GR).
